data.description: Fantastic investment potential with this two-family home. Each unit boasts two bedrooms and full bathroom. First floor unit has access to the basement. Separate basement laundry room w/separate washers and dryers for each unit. The property showcases hardwood floors in both units, along with recently renovated kitchens and updated bathrooms. Unit 2 is already leased to a tenant. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!HIGHEST AND BEST DUE BY Feb 27, 2024 at 10 AM
